{"tid":1012550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大年初一 四川男子因家庭糾紛殺死繼女殺傷岳母后跳樓自殺","createTime":"2019-02-07T16:14:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-08T03:16:53.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ab5c3205355d95f94aab3bcc8f4fdfd11fc92d8d","tid":1012550,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T16:14:02.000Z","msg":"據四川省南江縣公安局官方微博消息，2月5日，南江縣公安局110指揮中心接群眾報警稱：南江鎮光霧山大道城廟段樓上有人跳樓。經現場進一步勘察和初步調查核實：死者敬某安（男，51歲，南部縣人），因家庭糾紛，涉嫌在其位於南江鎮光霧山大道城廟段家中持刀將其繼女馮某某（女，24歲，南江縣大河鎮人）殺害，又將其岳母趙某某（女，81歲，南江縣大河鎮人）殺傷后，從其住所樓頂跳下畏罪自殺身亡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.news.sina.com.tw/article/20190206/29965674.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.news.sina.com.tw%2Farticle%2F20190206%2F29965674.html&d=HNFwsad0YdNlvWXbC%2BF%2Bcubr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=e067530d\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.news.sina.com.tw/article/20190206/29965674.html</a>"},{"pid":"87199f7afd7d037a7fb2c0025a884697060f2a8b","tid":1012550,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T16:25:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9d180dfdc4fbdba8fecc4f9b3de2180eda2b134e","tid":1012550,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T01:15:37.000Z","msg":"母后<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efc48b1b423f6a66de8928c721ae303fad02b314","tid":1012550,"uid":59283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T01:26:33.000Z","msg":"睇錯楊岳橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0db1eb6f53d1ac1c61d20a984eccbdabee0d162c","tid":1012550,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T01:59:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dce5be33199575781b3e8e54d84c7e27847b71b8","tid":1012550,"uid":23162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T03:16:53.000Z","msg":"其實做駙馬爺咪幾好，做乜咁傻殺咗岳母后呢，岳父皇傷心死啦"}]}